{"tid":260270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"螃蟹誤當生蠔　女沙灘裸曬陰部被夾傷","createTime":"2017-05-27T14:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T15:23:59.000Z","uid":35683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b69f4560b18c6f06c7f36e33ded339a6cf88a98","tid":260270,"uid":35683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"台灣蘋果新聞【生食動畫】螃蟹誤當生蠔　女沙灘裸曬陰部被夾傷 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新加坡一名28歲女子，在樟宜海灘做裸體日光浴時，下體被一隻螃蟹夾傷。專家認為，螃蟹可能誤以為女子下體是生蠔而施襲。<br />\n馬來西亞《中國報》報導，女子日前與2名女友人到沙灘曬太陽，趁四下無人時，她們把衣服脫光，盡情享受日光浴。曬了15分鐘後，女子突然感到下體劇痛，起身一看，驚見一隻大螃蟹用大螯夾著她下體不放，不禁大叫。她的朋友見狀，上前協助把螃蟹移開。因為擔心蟹螯有毒，友人還為女子「吸毒液」、清潔傷口，並聯絡醫護人員到場。<br />\n<br />\n女子傷勢沒有大礙，傷口很快復原，疤痕也不明顯，但心理創傷可能需要點時間才能平復。新加坡法例禁止在沙灘上裸體，醫護人員也勸傷者，以後不要再裸曬。<br />\n當地海洋生物學家說，螃蟹攻擊女性私處，是因為誤以為那是生蠔。他又說，蟹螯一般無毒，但若被夾地方很敏感，可能出現過敏反應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170527/1127404/?utm_source=Line&amp;utm_medium=iOS_Share&amp;utm_campaign=%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80/%E3%80%90%E7%94%9F%E9%A3%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E3%80%91%E8%9E%83%E8%9F%B9%E8%AA%A4%E7%95%B6%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E3%80%80%E5%A5%B3%E6%B2%99%E7%81%98%E8%A3%B8%E6%9B%AC%E9%99%B0%E9%83%A8%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%BE%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170527%2F1127404%2F%3Futm_source%3DLine%26utm_medium%3DiOS_Share%26utm_campaign%3D%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2595%25AB%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%259E%2583%25E8%259F%25B9%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E7%2595%25B6%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A0%2594%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2581%2598%25E8%25A3%25B8%25E6%259B%25AC%25E9%2599%25B0%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A4%25BE%25E5%2582%25B7&d=s2Vvds0Rqn8dD5jIACK6EgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=684056b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170527/1127404/?utm_source=Line&amp;utm_medium=iOS_Share&amp;utm_campaign=%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80/%E3%80%90%E7%94%9F%E9%A3%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E3%80%91%E8%9E%83%E8%9F%B9%E8%AA%A4%E7%95%B6%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E3%80%80%E5%A5%B3%E6%B2%99%E7%81%98%E8%A3%B8%E6%9B%AC%E9%99%B0%E9%83%A8%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%BE%E5%82%B7</a>"},{"pid":"478bc6fe319450b5aa9ad9040bda4caacfc42bad","tid":260270,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"Old news is so唔識串"},{"pid":"89ed48bc67131b1392e8cc963f8afdd6844d11bc","tid":260270,"uid":4672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"因為擔心蟹螯有毒，友人還為女子「吸毒液」、清潔傷口，並聯絡醫護人員到場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d65143b6c01b2a80cc45a71641b982984ec517","tid":260270,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為擔心蟹螯有毒，友人還為女子「吸毒液」、清潔傷口，並聯絡醫護人員到場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}